      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation and COU inputs not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Qualitative assessment confirms that validation inputs are representative of COU conditions. Formal equivalency scoring is deferred to MRL 3 assessments."
